Package: iLaplace
Type: Package
Title: Improved Laplace Approximation for Marginal Likelihoods
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2015-09-01
Authors@R: c(
       person("Erlis", "Ruli", email = "erlisr@yahoo.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
       person("Nicola", "Sartori", role = "aut"),
       person("Laura", "Ventura", role = "aut"))
Description: Improved Laplace approximation of Ruli et al. (2015) for integrals of concave and unimodal functions. The function requires user-supply R functions for: the integrand, its gradient and its Hessian matrix. The computations are run in parallel.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2), stats
